@ranmacwy Depends. 
For me it's a tie between Xenosaga 3 and Xenogears (love both of them very much). Xenosaga 2 is like Xenogears disc 2, except multiplied by 10. Xenosaga 1 drags a bit, but is a solid game. Most people tend to prefer Xenogears over any of the Xenosaga games, though.

I personally recommend playing all of the Xeno games, except Xenosaga 2, that one you can just watch all the cutscenes on youtube.
